Package application

Class Fulltime

java.lang.Object
application.Employee
application.Fulltime
Direct Known Subclasses:
Management
public class Fulltime
extends Employee
The fulltime class is a subclass of the employee superclass. It defines the specific attributes of a fulltime employee, such as their annual salary, and also calculates their pay for the current period.
Author:
Ceceliachollette-Dickson, Nidaansari
